{"type":"text","timestamp":1775872176445,"sessionID":"ses_285c5a73dffe6YuW2ZXWi3FUcT","part":{"id":"prt_d7a3ad024001r5QIBU4YxqY1jI","messageID":"msg_d7a3ac69c001wU75Uv1DYONb3f","sessionID":"ses_285c5a73dffe6YuW2ZXWi3FUcT","type":"text","text":"## AR-025: MetadataService 与数据模型 - Archive Summary\n\n### ✅ Completed\n\n**Phase 1: AgentMetadata Model**\n- Full Pydantic model with 22 fields in `metadata_service.py`\n- Field validators for `language`, `build_mode`, `port`\n- All core identification, build config, registry, runtime, and health probe fields\n\n**Phase 2: MetadataService Implementation**\n- `load_metadata()` with fallback chain (agent_metadata.yaml → agent.yaml → metadata.yaml)\n- `save_metadata()` with None-value exclusion\n- `update_metadata()` for partial updates\n- `validate_workspace()` with Python/Java validators\n\n**Phase 3: MetadataOptions Dataclass**\n- Complete dataclass in `pack_models.py` with 16 fields\n- `from_options()` classmethod for CLI dict mapping\n\n**Phase 4: PackRuntime Integration**\n- Full integration in `pack_runtime.py`\n- `_load_or_create_metadata()`, `_apply_option_overrides()` helpers\n- Complete `pack()` workflow using MetadataService\n- Dockerfile generation for Python/Java\n\n**Phase 5: Module Exports**\n- `StatusRuntime` exported in `agentcube/__init__.py`\n- All runtimes properly exported in `agentcube/runtime/__init__.py`\n\n**Phase 6-7: Unit Tests**\n- 5 tests for `AgentMetadata` (validation, defaults)\n- 7 tests for `MetadataService` (save/load, fallbacks, updates, validation)\n- 6 tests for `MetadataOptions`\n\n---\n\n### ⏳ Deferred\n\n**Phase 9: Integration Tests**\n- T9.1-9.3: End-to-end PackRuntime integration tests\n\n**Phase 10: Code Quality**\n- T10.1-10.5: mypy, ruff, coverage verification, backward compatibility tests\n\n**Phase 11: Documentation**\n- T11.1-11.5: Comprehensive docstrings, example `agent_metadata.yaml`, README updates\n\n**Validation & Edge Cases** (from AR-022 Phase 5)\n- CLI-level validation for URLs, node_port ranges\n- Enhanced error logging","time":{"start":1775872176442,"end":1775872176442}}}
